('y-combinator','Y Combinator','accelerator','accel','Y Combinator is the world’s number one accelerator for startups. The most notable startups from the program include Airbnb and Stripe. Y Combinator run two batches of companies per year. Check out their website for application deadline.

The winter batch runs from **January to March**, while the summer batch takes place from **June–August** usually. The demo day is an invite-only event for startups and investors and runs In April for winter batch and September for summer batch each year.

**Program terms:**

They invest $500,000 in every company on standard terms. Their $500K investment is made on 2 separate safes: invest $125,000 on a post-money safe in return for 7% of your company (the “$125k safe”), invest $375,000 on an uncapped safe with a Most Favored Nation (“MFN”) provision (the “MFN safe”).

According to its site, Y Combinator invests US, Cayman, Singapore, and Canada corporations. They have founders who apply to YC from all around the world and many have already incorporated in their home countries.

Y combinator introduces founders to lawyers who can work out the best process for creating a company (or parent company) in a jurisdiction in which we can invest. Often, founders will keep their original entity as a subsidiary of a new parent company and the original entity will continue to operate in their home country.

Non-profits startups will receive a donation of $100k without receiving anything in return for their donation.','https://www.ycombinator.com','https://fundingcake.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/FundingCake-Logo-Startup-Grants.png','Y Combinator','San Francisco','US',NULL,ARRAY['global-startup-accelerators','portfolio-jobs']::TEXT[],'{"apply_url":null,"category_labels":["San Francisco Accelerators","San Francisco Meetups","San Francisco Venture Capital","San Francisco 🇺🇸🌉"],"category_slugs":["san-francisco-startup-accelerators-incubators","san-francisco-meetups","san-francisco-venture-capital","san-francisco"],"completeness":1.0,"equity_pct":null,"fundingcake_program_type":"accelerator","fundingcake_url":"https://fundingcake.com/listing/y-combinator/","money_terms":["$100k","$125,000","$125k","$375,000","$500,000","$500K"],"socials":{"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/YCombinator","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/ycombinator/","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/school/y-combinator/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/ycombinator"},"tag_labels":["global startup accelerators","portfolio jobs"]}'::JSONB,'fundingcake'),
